      "content": "hey so i was cutting veggies and the knife slipped, i have a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s still oozing a bit but it’s not like spraying blood or anything. would it be okay if i just put some honey on it and wrap it up with a bandage? i really don't want to go to the clinic tonight if i can help it.",
