      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried pressure but it definitely still leaks out whenever i move it. like it's deep enough that i can see the edges of the skin pulling apart a bit. is the honey thing still a good idea though? i read online that medical grade honey can actually act like a barrier and help it close up faster without having to deal with doctors and all that. feels like something i could just handle myself if i have the right stuff.",
