    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just looked at the butterfly strips online and they seem kinda complicated to use properly. honestly i'm just trying to avoid the clinic cuz it's so expensive and the wait times are crazy. if i just use a thick layer of that honey and keep it wrapped really tight with a bandage, wouldn't that basically do the same thing as a stitch by holding it in place? i really just want to fix this here tonight so i can sleep.",
